tBuffer.limit());\n        assertThat(Arrays.copyOfRange(outputStream.toByteArray(), 2, 6)).containsExactly(1, 2, 3, 4);\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 837, "output": 2227, "cacheRead": 35840, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 38904, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1779383350682, "responseId": "resp_04bc299b8b533de2016a0f3c374728819db233fa8f800bdbe4"}}
